'''Justin.tv'''，于2007年3月建立，創辦人為[[簡彥豪|簡彥豪]]。總部位于美國加利福尼亞州舊金山。它是一個可即時聊天的個人線上音樂與[[影音串流|影音串流]]平台。

2011年6月，分割出聚焦於電子遊戲直播的網站「[[Twitch|Twitch]]」。2014年2月，Twitch.tv與Justin.Tv的母公司改名為「Twitch Interactive」<ref name="twitchint">{{cite web |url= http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/210384/Twitch_parent_company_rebrands_as_Twitch_Interactive.php |title= Twitch parent company rebrands as Twitch Interactive |publisher= Mike Rose |accessdate= 2014-02-10 |archive-date= 2014-02-22 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140222204141/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/210384/Twitch_parent_company_rebrands_as_Twitch_Interactive.php |dead-url= no }}</ref>。同年8月5日，Justin.tv終止服務<ref name="shut1">{{cite web |publisher=Justin.TV |title=Goodbye from Justin.tv |url=http://justin.tv/ |date=2014-08-05 |accessdate=2014-08-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=http://arquivo.pt/wayback/20081022071152/http://www.justin.tv/ |archivedate=2008-10-22 }}</ref><ref name="shut2">{{cite news |publisher=Arstechnica |last=Machovech |first=Sam |date=2014-08-05 |title=Streaming video site Justin.tv announces closure effective immediately |url=http://arstechnica.com/gaming/2014/08/streaming-video-site-justin-tv-announces-closure-effective-immediately/ |accessdate=2015-11-17 |archive-date=2014-08-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140807223009/http://arstechnica.com/gaming/2014/08/streaming-video-site-justin-tv-announces-closure-effective-immediately/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="shut3">{{cite news |publisher=The Verge |last=Popper |first=Ben |date=2014-08-05 |title=Justin.tv, the live video pioneer that birthed Twitch, officially shuts down |url=http://www.theverge.com/2014/8/5/5971939/justin-tv-the-live-video-pioneer-that-birthed-twitch-officially-shuts |accessdate=2015-11-17 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111225732/http://www.theverge.com/2014/8/5/5971939/justin-tv-the-live-video-pioneer-that-birthed-twitch-officially-shuts |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

